  "scientificName": "Docosahexaenoic Acid (DHA), Eicosapentaenoic Acid (EPA) / ω-3 fatty acids",
  "family": null,
  "genus": null,
  "description": {
    "en": "Omega 3 fatty acids are found in cold-water fish including tuna, salmon and mackerel. Plant sources include dark green leafy vegetables, flaxseed oils and certain vegetable oils.\n",
    "zh-Hant": "奧米加3（學名：Docosahexaenoic Acid (DHA), Eicosapentaenoic Acid (EPA) / ω-3 fatty acids）是一種具有藥用價值的天然產物。現代藥理學研究證實其含有多種生物活性成分，在傳統醫學和現代保健領域均有重要應用價值。",
    "zh-Hans": "奧米加3（学名：Docosahexaenoic Acid (DHA), Eicosapentaenoic Acid (EPA) / ω-3 fatty acids）是一种具有药用價值的天然產物。現代药理学研究证实其含有多种生物活性成分，在传统医学和現代保健領域均有重要应用價值。"
  },
